name: Dokar Venas
content: Dokar Venas was a male individual who served the criminal gang the Strus clan on the planet Jakku around the time of the outbreak of the First Order-Resistance War. After word reached the Strus clan that a group of nomads had discovered a secret treasure within the wreck of the Starlight Wanderer, a New Republic CR90 corvette that had crashed on Jakku many years earlier, Venas led a group of Strus clan enforcers that attacked the nomads in an attempt to access the Starlight Wanderer crash site.
